response.overview: On November 24th GCW at WrestleCade Weekend 2023 is live on FITE+ straight from Benton Convention Center in Winston-Salem, NC. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Billie Starkz.  Also in the lineup:  Jordan Oliver vs Masha Slamovich  Maki Itoh vs Kenzie Paige  Six Man Tag Team Match  George South & The Mortons (Kerry Morton & Ricky Morton) vs Insane Clown Bussy (Allie Katch, Effy & Violent J)  Matt Cardona w/ Steph De Lander vs Mike Bailey  Mike Jackson vs Santana Jackson  Joey Janela vs Mance Warner
response.title: GCW at WrestleCade Weekend
